	<conclusion><title> üì§ Wrap-Up </title>

		<paragraphs><title> Summary </title>
			<p>
				<ul>
					<li>Equilibrium solutions are constant solutions <m>y(t) = c</m> where <m>f(c) = 0</m>.</li>
					<li>In the slope field, these show up as rows of horizontal slope segments.</li>
					<li>To find them, solve <m>f(y) = 0</m>.</li>
				</ul>
			</p>
		</paragraphs>

		<paragraphs><title> Reading Questions </title>
